---
title: The Great Caper: Cod Piccata with Couscous and Baby Spinach
description: Piccata may sound like a fancy Italian dish that only your nonna can do right. But really, all it demands is swirling lemon, capers, herbs, and butter in a pan until they come together in tart and tangy harmony. Here, we’re drizzling the combo over flaky cod, tender spinach, and bubbly couscous so that they soak up all that amazing flavor.
